I believe in YOU. You are SO powerful🌟🌎🫂 #44daystofreedom

It is not selfish to follow your dreams and deepest desires. In fact it’s your sacred responsibility. 

Every day you go without pursuit of your dreams is a day where earth doesn’t get to receive your deepest purest medicine. If you feel stuck, feel like you don’t have the time, feel like your time is being sucked into something that doesn’t light you up, then it’s time for you to seek a life of FREEDOM. 

What if you didn’t have to trade your time for money? Would that open up TIME and SPACE for you to go after your dreams? What if you worked in community and leveraged your time to FREE yourself up and pour your heart and soul into your longings and deepest desires?? 

It’s through creating freedom for yourself that you can pour your medicine and magic into the world. 

We ALL have our own unique medicine to offer. Are you ready to share yours with the world?? 

Comment “dreams” to confirm to the world that you are ready to start taking yours more seriously! ☁️ Better yet, share some of your dreams, visions, and deepest longings in the comments!! 🤸🏼‍♀️

We often spend so much time focusing on understanding the world around us, but neglect the process of fully understanding ourself. The biggest shift is looking within and realizing life is coming OUT OF YOU, not at you… When you create a deep bond with yourself, it doesn’t matter what the outside world thinks, you know THE TRUTH. ✨

From a young age, we’re conditioned to seek answers outside of ourselves, in books, classrooms, and the wisdom of others. While external sources of knowledge are undeniably valuable, the greatest insights often resides within your very being. Your intuition, that inner compass, is one of the most powerful tools you possess. 📖

When you tap into your intuition, you open a direct line of communication with your deepest self, the repository of your unique experiences, feelings, and desires. You just know. Your body knows. This inner wisdom isn’t clouded by external biases or preconceived notions. It’s a pure, unfiltered stream of consciousness that can guide you through the complexities of life. 🌬️

So, remember, the journey within is the path to true liberation and self-discovery. Trust in your intuition, connect with your inner self, and you’ll find that the answers you seek are not elusive mysteries hidden in the world around you, but powerful revelations thriving within you. 🧚🏼

An aggressive loving reminder for you😁🫶🏼 My repetitive negative thoughts were holding me back for sooo long… and I didn’t even realize it cus they became so normal. I decided to look at my mind with curiosity and compassion as I investigated these deep rooted thoughts and emotions.. I stepped out of the victim mentality and realized the only one holding me back was ME. We are all capable of creating the life we want, but until you start believing that you deserve it, it won’t happen. I encourage you to start noticing what thoughts consistently pop up throughout your day. Write them down. Don’t judge yourself just investigate :)) When did you first start believing this? Is it your thought or someone else’s?? If you want to dive deeper, send me a dm🤍

A time for rest and reflection <3 Moments pass so quickly, take time for yourself to think about the past year. Look into your mind with curiosity, celebrate your wins (big and small), send love to your body that has gotten you this far. Some questions to ask🫶🏼 How have I changed/grown? What have I learned about myself? What were the hardest challenges I faced? What lessons did I learn? What am I letting go of? What do I want to add into my life? How do I want to show up in the world? When am I the happiest? Who do I feel my best around? How can I step out of my comfort zone? ✨✨✨ This year has been the most challenging, yet the most magical. I love stepping back with a wide perspective of the year, cherishing the highest highs and embracing even the darkest moments. We can learn so much through our own life, every experience has a message in it. Feeling so grateful for another year🤍

I love the feeling of being weightless, getting to explore a world that isn’t my own. I feel free of thoughts, my mind is fully entranced by the life in front of me. My worries slip away as fish swim past of me. I feel freeeeee, reminded that there are infinite realities happening everywhere all the time. Life isn’t changing because I am looking at it, it has nothing to do with me, I just get the opportunity to experience it🫧

✨You are made of magic💫✨
